title: The Implementation Plan of Guiding University Students’ Entrepreneurship Release... (Xuzhou Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Xuzhou Municipal Government ) On September 22 , the Implementation Plan of Guiding University Students’ Entrepreneurship ( 2015 —2017) was released. According to the plan, Xuzhou will assist and guide more than 3000 university students
